					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plilt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(876026); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=876026&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610163877" alt="Plilt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=876026)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plilt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(876026); return false;" >Plilt</a></span> <span class="odate time_1324171309 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">18 Dec 2011 01:21</span>
