			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1330291">
									

<p>Think of it this way: The Foundation has seen no choice but to do horrible things. Now they have a choice. Their mandate hasn't changed, but 682's actions have enabled them to do things differently. And I can also see the Foundation throwing its hands up after the Rampage and deciding that the new world needs a new approach, now that amensiacs are kind of pointless, other organizations have an increase in membership&#8230;</p>
<p>If it's a brave new world, then perhaps it requires a brave new Foundation.</p>

